# RF24Gateway #

A complimentary library to **RF24Ethernet**, for _RPi/Linux devices_.

**RF24Ethernet** allows small Arduino/AVR devices to communicate using TCP/IP over _**NRF24L01(+)** radio modules_.

**RF24Gateway** allows a RPi/Linux device to act as a gateway for those nodes, handling IP traffic automatically, while allowing users
to utilize standard RF24Network messages as well.

